Class NetworkTopologyExecutor

  • java.lang.Object
    • repast.simphony.engine.graph.AbstractGraphExecutor<java.lang.Object>
      • repast.simphony.engine.graph.NetworkTopologyExecutor

    Executor<GraphParams<java.lang.Object>>, GraphExecutor<java.lang.Object>

    public class NetworkTopologyExecutor
extends AbstractGraphExecutor<java.lang.Object>
    Executor for NetworkTopologies. This validates nodes' execution by checking to make sure they are still connected.

                               Traverser<java.lang.Object> traverser,

                               Network topology)
        Constructs this executor to execute using the given schedule and node execution parameters. This class primarily is interested in the topology as it uses it for validation, the rest of the parameters are used by the super class.
        Parameters:
        schedule - the schedule to schedule itself with
        baseParams - the parameters for the scheduling
        traverser - the traverser for traversing the graph
        nodeExecutor - the executor for executing nodes
        topology - the topology to use to determine if nodes are connected
